HEADWORD: Circination
<hw>Cir`ci*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>circinatio</ets> circle.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>An orbicular motion.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>bailey.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
